---
title: Bacon & Parsley Crumbed Pork Tenderloin with Parmesan Roast Potatoes, Pear Salad & Mayonnaise
description: A pub-style dinner demands all the works, like a herby bacon topping to go on crumbed pork. Working its way up to being our favourite addition are the sliced and roasted cheesy potatoes, they really make your mouth water!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6529014cb776085eb7bd8afb-23e73eaa.jpeg
